WEBVTT

00:00.002 --> 00:01.421
Previously on <i>The Royals...</i>

00:01.484 --> 00:03.703
<i>I spent a lot of time
in my brother's shadow,</i>

00:03.789 --> 00:05.898
<i>but it wasn't okay the day I met you.</i>

00:05.960 --> 00:07.628
Bagsy, Sparrow.

00:07.855 --> 00:09.252
If she was my girl, I wouldn't hide her.

00:09.276 --> 00:11.664
I'm a royal. She's not.

00:11.736 --> 00:13.277
How could you? These letters

00:13.324 --> 00:16.303
were supposed to be between us. Not us!

00:16.566 --> 00:18.557
Don't ever doubt your words again,
they're perfect.

00:18.581 --> 00:20.093
Just believe in them.

00:21.187 --> 00:22.367
(CYRUS) You tricked me.

00:22.434 --> 00:25.640
If you think I'm giving up
my reign without a fight,

00:25.724 --> 00:27.523
you'd better watch your back.

00:27.791 --> 00:30.914
<i> # Kingliam seems to be everywhere.</i>

00:31.195 --> 00:33.484
Simon is your biological father.

00:33.601 --> 00:35.468
I need you to believe in me now.

00:35.609 --> 00:37.792
This is your last night as King.

00:38.136 --> 00:39.945
Things are gonna change for you now.

00:40.062 --> 00:42.445
Things are gonna change for us.

