00:53.726 --> 00:55.159
Robby?

01:00.928 --> 01:03.210
Hello, Mum.

01:08.957 --> 01:12.067
<font color=#FF00FF>*THE ROYALS*</font>
<font color=#00FF00>Season 03 Episode 04</font>
<font color=#FFFF00>"Our (Late) Dear Brother's Death"</font>
